sentence: What does a pescatarian librarian eat when theyre hungry for a little snack? microfiche.
explanation: A microfiche is a flat piece of film containing microphotographs of the pages of a document.
first_new_sentence: The library has rows of microfiche that make it easy to archive information.
second_new_sentence: Microfiche can be used to store detailed records in a compact and convenient format.
